<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Evolutionary_psychology&amp;action=edit&amp;section=26" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/David_Buss" title="David Buss">Buss, D. M.</a> (1995). Evolutionary psychology: A new paradigm for psychological science. <i>Psychological Inquiry, 6,</i> 1-30. <a href="http://homepage.psy.utexas.edu/homepage/Group/BussLAB/pdffiles/ANewParadigmforPsych.PDF" class="external text" title="http://homepage.psy.utexas.edu/homepage/Group/BussLAB/pdffiles/ANewParadigmforPsych.PDF" rel="nofollow">Full text</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Durrant, R., &amp; Ellis, B.J. (2003). Evolutionary Psychology. In M. Gallagher &amp; R.J. Nelson (Eds.), <i>Comprehensive Handbook of Psychology, Volume Three: Biological Psychology</i> (pp. 1-33). New York: Wiley &amp; Sons. <a href="http://media.wiley.com/product_data/excerpt/38/04713840/0471384038.pdf#search='evolutionary%20psychologypdf'" class="external text" title="http://media.wiley.com/product_data/excerpt/38/04713840/0471384038.pdf#search='evolutionary%20psychologypdf'" rel="nofollow">Full text</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/John_Tooby" title="John Tooby">Tooby, J.</a> &amp; <a href="/wiki/Leda_Cosmides" title="Leda Cosmides">Cosmides, L.</a> (2005). Conceptual foundations of evolutionary psychology. In D. M. Buss (Ed.), <i>The Handbook of Evolutionary Psychology</i> (pp. 5-67). Hoboken, NJ: Wiley. <a href="http://www.psych.ucsb.edu/research/cep/papers/bussconceptual05.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.psych.ucsb.edu/research/cep/papers/bussconceptual05.pdf" rel="nofollow">Full text</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>For more readings, see the <a href="http://hbes.com/Hbes/books_c.htm" class="external text" title="http://hbes.com/Hbes/books_c.htm" rel="nofollow">books</a> page at the <a href="http://hbes.com/" class="external text" title="http://hbes.com/" rel="nofollow">Human Behavior and Evolution Society</a></li>
</ul>
